{
  "stem": "8252.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have to mention that at this point already, I established a connection which my father in-- in America, and I was getting cigarettes sent from Canada by thousands.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was a currency in Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I could buy a piece of lard or a piece of-- or-- or a chicken or something like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my best friend in camp, who was a tailor from Strasburg, Abe Gross, was a very good cook, so that we cooked for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We cooked the things that I could get and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was in rather privileged position, because I-- I had this freedom of being around, and I was being loaded by either German political prisoners or by Russians, loaded and unloaded.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were barracks, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- the room was for about 20-- 20 men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was bunks, the same you've seen from Auschwitz, the same type of bunks, only we had-- we had so much better life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We cannot compare our suffering to theirs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were deprived of liberty, but they were deprived of life, so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only Yugos-- Yugoslav, French, and Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "French.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "French.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yugoslavs, of course, didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of them did because some of the people from Belgrade, from capital of Yugoslavia, the Jews from capital all spoke French.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But French was our language inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were not too far from an officer camp-- officer's camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's how my career in that camp ended.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From an officer's camp, and they had radios.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were passing the information to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were some of our people who had some kind of work to do in the officer's camp, and they would bring out that information.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
